  "title": "CAD Drafter",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>1. Develop and maintain CAD Drawings</p><p>2. Develop dimensional drawings for layouts and non-dimensional drawings</p><p>3. Revise drawings based on instructions/comments from engineers</p><p>4. Communicate effectively and work closely with the design team members of individual’s project assignment</p><p>5. Responsible for receiving, registering, filling and distribution of documents for the detailed engineering section</p><p>6. Develop computer generated drawings, isometrics, details, plans, schedules and data sheets</p><p>7. Perform other related work duties as assigned by Reporting Supervisor</p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><p>Ø Diploma/ Degree in Architecture</p><p>Ø Civil Engineering with Minimum 5 Years of relevant working experience in Singapore.</p><p>Ø Preferred Candidates with LTA project experience</p>",
